snippet.title: The Sims 3 Showtime Katy Perry CE The One That Got Away
snippet.description: Make your rise to fame in The Sims 3 Showtime Katy Perry Collector's Edition with unique Katy Perry themed in-game content and an exclusive poster.  Your Sim can become a superstar singer, acrobat, magician... and even moonlight as a DJ. New, optional social features allow you to connect with friends, and share your big moments through in-game news feeds, messaging, and live updates.
